{"tid":2297382,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王婆婆今午提堂准保釋 庭上投訴警員曾向她動武 導致手臂瘀傷","createTime":"2020-11-23T08:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T15:28:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"e85461f21bdb0910a24df1c6c8032c860b8d84ca","tid":2297382,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:50:31.000Z","msg":"「王婆婆」王鳳瑤，被指去年1月在高等法院接受安檢期間，衝撞一名保安員，導致保安胸口發紅。事隔近兩年後，警方以普通襲擊罪名拘控王婆婆。案件上周六提堂前，王婆婆報稱不適，留院至今午被押解往東區裁判法院應訊。王投訴被捕時及在警署羈留期間遭警員不當對待，導致受傷，更要兩度入院。裁判官應辯方申請，押後案件再訊，並批准王婆婆以100元保釋。<br />\n<br />\n王婆婆今午身穿厚外套，臉上略顯疲態，由兩名女庭警押解出庭。王婆婆出庭時向主任裁判官錢禮鞠躬，聽取控罪後輕聲表示明白內容。<br />\n<br />\n辯方投訴指，被告遭警員拘捕以及羈留警署期間，均曾被警員施加不當對待，導致受傷，需要在上周六及周日先後送往聯合醫院及瑪麗醫院，惟庭上沒有透露受傷詳情。裁判官將事件記錄在案。據悉，警員拘捕被告時曾向她動武，導致她手臂瘀傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201123/OLOCRGYVGRF75DDECMYJEIXYEU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2FOLOCRGYVGRF75DDECMYJEIXYEU%2F&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnWg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=e62919a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2FOLOCRGYVGRF75DDECMYJEIXYEU%2F&h=71ebfc06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201123/OLOCRGYVGRF75DDECMYJEIXYEU/</a>"},{"pid":"342e307d839e8027137cb657020062f7f71a19de","tid":2297382,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decc2a5ebc918535493c3c33fc0e89cea20753fb","tid":2297382,"uid":11291,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:53:03.000Z","msg":"身為警員郁手郁腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港警察知法犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20637a38e1a0076461c03bb7abc3